{"parentUuid":"28a18345-5787-4b99-8914-4750765c8c6c","isSidechain":false,"message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_vrtx_016Gyu2yK9JtgpnSj7td4drr","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"靠，这问题问得好，爹。\n\n`claude --resume` 出来一坨没名字的会话确实他妈的难找。你可以这样搞：\n\n**启动时用 `--name` 命名：**\n```bash\nclaude --name \"oa-考勤bug修复\"\nclaude --name \"hr-绩效模块重构\"\n```\n\n**恢复时直接按名字找：**\n```bash\nclaude --resume \"oa-考勤bug修复\"\n```\n\n或者 `claude --resume` 弹出列表时，有名字的会话一眼就能认出来。\n\n**建议命名规范：**\n- `项目名-模块-任务`，比如 `oa-审批-添加抄送功能`\n- 简短但能区分就行，别写小作文\n\n所以是的，**每次开新会话都命名一下**，花1秒钟，省你后面翻半天。\n\n---\n\n**改动总结：** 本次无代码改动，回答了 Claude Code 会话命名的使用建议。要不要我把这条加到你的 CLAUDE.md 或 memory 里提醒你？"}],"stop_reason":"end_turn","stop_sequence":null,"stop_details":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":3,"cache_creation_input_tokens":32220,"cache_read_input_tokens":0,"output_tokens":380,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":32220},"inference_geo":"","iterations":[],"speed":"standard"}},"type":"assistant","uuid":"73813fd3-3910-45c8-87f0-4120ec6ce8cd","timestamp":"2026-04-08T02:12:45.809Z","userType":"external","entrypoint":"cli","cwd":"D:\\project\\info-gitlab\\oa","sessionId":"6cfcb0e3-35d7-4ef0-ba0a-0a24d3207550","version":"2.1.78","gitBranch":"HEAD"}
